\

\f0\b\fs36 \cf3 Osc(table, freq, phase, mul, add) \cf0 - 
\f1\b0\fs28 a \cf3 Ugen\cf0  that implements a table-lookup oscillator  It outputs samples successively chosen from a predefined array of floating-point numbers, stored in a Buffer.  The table is specified by its Buffer index, which is an integer.\

\f0\b\fs36 \cf3 SinOsc(freq, phase, mul, add) \cf0 - 
\f1\b0\fs28 a \cf3 Osc with a sinewave of 8096 samples as its Wavetable.\cf0 \
\

