\cf3 In\cf0  the\cf3  SuperCollide\cf0 r application, a \cf3 Routine\cf0  can be played using a \cf3 Clock\cf0 .  Every time the \cf3 Routine\cf0  yields, it should do so with a float, the clock will interpret that, usually pausing for that many seconds, and then resume the routine, passing it it the clock's current time.\
The default clock is the SystemClock.\cf4 \
